182
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:49,000
 it develops through specific experiences

183
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:51,000
 and cognitive frameworks.

184
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:54,000
 So we learn that in life, that we're a victim.

185
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:58,000
 This mindset is characterized by a persistent belief

186
00:07:58,000 --> 00:08:03,000
 that one is powerless against negative circumstances,

187
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:05,000
 attributing hardships to external forces

188
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:10,000
